== Steve Blake == Steve Blake sraral hya'ga sisyow na NBA, wal malaxmisoq qaniy la. kawas tay 1980, ryax sa tay 26 nqo tay 2, Steve Blake, sqoliq na p'onro. pincyowagan nya' Washington Wizards (2003–2005) Kawas tay2003, galan tay 38 lpgan sisyow na v qo Steve Blake. 5.9 tinso' wal galon ni Terrell Brandon. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players
